3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper involves the analysis of graph structures and the development of combinatorial algorithms, which are core topics in discrete mathematics. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the time and space complexity of triangle counting algorithms, which is a central topic in computational complexity theory.
